&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;ARIEL, Wash. (Oct. 23, 2025) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family:lato,lato_embeddedfont,lato_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&mdash; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;A new fee structure will go into effect at Pacific Power&rsquo;s recreation sites on the Lewis River early next month.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:calibri,calibri_embeddedfont,calibri_msfontservice,sans-serif; font-size:11pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
